channel.title: I can't run a ip-changer client, why?
channel.description:
When I try to run a 508 ip changer client, this is the message that comes up. 'java' is not recognized as an internal or external command, operable program or batch file. Press any key to continue . . .
why does that happen? can any1 tell me how to fix it please. thanks.
